<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Global Terrorism Index Analysis</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <script src="script.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Global Terrorism Index Analysis</h1>
        <p>Understanding the trends and impacts of terrorism worldwide.</p>
    </header>
    
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#overview">Overview</a></li>
            <li><a href="#trends">Trends</a></li>
            <li><a href="#impact">Impact</a></li>
            <li><a href="#conclusion">Conclusion</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section id="overview">
            <h2>Overview</h2>
            <p>The Global Terrorism Index (GTI) measures the impact of terrorism on countries around the world.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="trends">
            <h2>Trends</h2>
            <div class="chart-container">
                <canvas id="trendsChart"></canvas>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="impact">
            <h2>Impact</h2>
            <p>The impact of terrorism varies significantly across regions and countries.</p>
            <div class="impact-cards">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Region A</h3>
                    <p>Details about the impact in Region A.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Region B</h3>
                    <p>Details about the impact in Region B.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Region C</h3>
                    <p>Details about the impact in Region C.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="conclusion">
            <h2>Conclusion</h2>
            <p>Summarizing the findings and implications of the Global Terrorism Index.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 Global Terrorism Index Analysis</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>